  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK660">
<l>calattāṟ poruḷceytē mārttal pacumaṭ</l>
<l> kalattuṇīr peytirīi yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>(For a minister) to protect (his king) with wealth obtained by foul means is like preserving a vessel of wet clay by filling it with water.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
